definitions.definition: A person who sets type ; a typesetter .
One who, or that which, composes or sets in order.
examples: I work as an image compositor .

definitions.definition: A system that puts images together in a buffer (such as individual windows on a desktop ) to generate a final display image.

main_definition: A person who sets type ; a typesetter .
secondary_definitions: One who, or that which, composes or sets in order.
( computer graphics ) A system that puts images together in a buffer (such as individual windows on a desktop ) to generate a final display image.
